<emphasis id="4BE5533FA714D6CF3206D3F10C2E6A3A" bold="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="139">Figure 8.</emphasis>
Map showing distribution of genera in the family 
<taxonomicName id="22EF35DC35934E417C6A6C3690D43530" authorityName="Myers &amp; Lowry" authorityYear="2020" class="Malacostraca" family="Protorchestiidae" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="" order="Amphipoda" pageId="0" pageNumber="139" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="family">Protorchestiidae</taxonomicName>
.
